Package: cloneMap
Title: A Package to Construct Visual Representations of the Spatial Distribution of Somatic Clones in a Tissue / Sample   
Version: 1.0.0.0
Date: 2020-08-22
Author: Alexander M Frankell <alexander.frankell@crick.ac.uk>
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexander",
           family = "Frankell",
           role = "cre",
           email = "alexander.frankell@crick.ac.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0341-7878"))
Maintainer: Alexander M Frankell <alexander.frankell@crick.ac.uk>
Description: Makes representations of somatic clones present in a tissue accounting for clone size, i.e. the Cancer Cell Fraction (CCF), and for phylogenetic relationships between clones in a semi-randomised but reproducible manner.
License: MIT + file LICENCE 
Encoding: UTF-8
